quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  26,1,Tâ-Sîn-Mîm
  26,2,Ezi ziiVesi zeNcwadi ecacileyo
  26,3,Mhlawumbi wena (Muhammad) ungazibulala ngenxa yobuhlungu bokuba bangangabi ngawo amakholwa
  26,4,Ukuba beSithanda beSingabathumelela umqondiso ovela esibhakabhakeni obuza kubenza iintamo zabo zihlale zithobekile
  26,5,Kananjalo akukho siTyhilelo sitsha esifika kubo sivela eNkosini yabo abangasitshikileliyo
  26,6,"Ke kaloku bona baphikile, kodwa kuza kufika iindaba kubo zoko babedla ngokukugxeka"
  26,7,Kanti abawujongi na umhlaba (babone) ukuba Sihlumise kangakanani na kuhlobo ngalunye (izinto) zodidi oluxabisekileyo
  26,8,"Inene, kuko oku kukho umqondiso, kodwa uninzi lwabo abangomakholwa"
  26,9,"Yaye inene, iNkosi yakho nguSobunganga, uSozinceba"